demo

demo

    Description:
        demo app to get table information from databases

    Syntax:
        $ demo 

    Subcommands:
        fetch:
            show information of tables

        list:
            list tables


demo fetch

    Description:
        show information of tables

    Syntax:
        $ demo fetch [<option>|<argument>]... [-- [<argument>]...]

    Options:
        -config=<string>, -c=<string>  (default=""):
            path to config file

        -verbose[=<boolean>], -v[=<boolean>]  (default=false):
            shows detailed log

    Arguments:
        1. [<tables:string>]...
            names of tables to be described


demo list

    Description:
        list tables

    Syntax:
        $ demo list [<option>]...

    Options:
        -config=<string>, -c=<string>  (default=""):
            path to config file


